Do this first:

Under 'Source Packages', right click on the package name 'uk.ac.tees.username'

Select REFACTOR

Select RENAME

Delete 'username' and insert your actual username.

Repeat for 'Test Packages', if required.



You are ready to start!



HINT: You can run all tests by right clicking on the project name and selecting TEST. This will
get you a lot of error messages, because you have not written the classes yet.

HINT: You can run a single file of tests by right clicking on that test file and selecting 'Test File'.

If I were developing a solution, I would start by creating Cadet, Soldier and Killable, then testing them.